recordedBy: Daphne Stone
locality: Mt. Baker-Snoqualmie National Forest, Skykomish Ranger District, Beckler Thin Unit 55A. From Hwy 2, drive N on Rd 65 1.8 mi to the N end of Unit 55A. Walk W from flag along the N boundary of the unit approx 775\\' to site. Site marked by one set of 2 flags labeled 'NEBE-DS-1'. Nearby is an old square post w/ rusted metal sign on it. Flag on rd is orange and white striped and indicates site is 333\\' from rd at 270 deg. Distance on flagging is wrong! Site is in or just outside pointed NW corner of unit.
